322
00:26:05,960 --> 00:26:07,519
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje se onda rodila ta...

323
00:26:07,519 --> 00:26:11,279
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, mi živimo u civilizaciji u ovome vremenu u kojem jesmu,

324
00:26:11,480 --> 00:26:15,480
[SPEAKER_01] u kojem je dominantna dimenzija postojanja sebičnosti.

325
00:26:15,480 --> 00:26:17,640
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je u svim porama devuštva.

326
00:26:17,640 --> 00:26:19,400
[SPEAKER_01] I ona je u svim razmišljanjima.

327
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi to možda stavio u onaj citada koji kaže da

328
00:26:23,900 --> 00:26:27,019
[SPEAKER_01] teška vremena stvaraju jake ljude.

329
00:26:27,019 --> 00:26:31,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ali jaki ljudi stvaraju jednostavno vremena.

330
00:26:31,519 --> 00:26:32,640
[SPEAKER_01] Laka vremena.

331
00:26:32,640 --> 00:26:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] A onda laka vremena stvaraju loše ljude.

332
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:39,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim nešto ima u tome.

333
00:26:39,500 --> 00:26:48,099
[SPEAKER_01] Mi smo zapljusnuti s ovim što je zapad ili Europa postala

334
